  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1399380/extras/59b733aef714f258c27b8268e43cd328.avif?t=1603896637\" width=616 height=120 /></span><br><br>NUI is a game about farewell, a minimalistic puzzle-platformer where a mysterious character carries a sword deeply tied to him. <br><br>The sword must be taken to the end of the cave, while the sword limits the character movements, it can also be used as a powerful weapon. However, due to the bond with the sword distancing too much from it will damage you...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1399380/extras/ea55620a3199f4afebdaac107dd706db.avif?t=1603896637\" width=616 height=120 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A small puzzle-platformer with a minimalistic and touching story about farewell.<br></li><li>Discover the way to carry your sword to the end of each screen<br></li><li>Explore an ancient cave with 50 levels that mix platforming skills and puzzles<br></li><li>More than 15 secrets scattered through the cave to be found<br></li><li>Small Game: Main game can be completed in less than 1 hour</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1399380/extras/1f9a766d493b06584b68bb03384c58af.avif?t=1603896637\" width=616 height=120 /></span><br><br>NUI is a small passion project made in our free time, for that reason, it is meant to be a short and fun experience.<br>Let us here your thoughts and suggestions about it! Contact us by any of the links available at <br>Have fun playing it!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1399380/extras/30a4ecbe94af55b54f6b1652a459f42d.poster.avif?t=1603896637\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1399380/extras/30a4ecbe94af55b54f6b1652a459f42d.webm?t=1603896637\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1399380/extras/30a4ecbe94af55b54f6b1652a459f42d.mp4?t=1603896637\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1399380/extras/59b733aef714f258c27b8268e43cd328.avif?t=1603896637\" width=616 height=120 /></span><br><br>NUI is a game about farewell, a minimalistic puzzle-platformer where a mysterious character carries a sword deeply tied to him. <br><br>The sword must be taken to the end of the cave, while the sword limits the character movements, it can also be used as a powerful weapon. However, due to the bond with the sword distancing too much from it will damage you...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1399380/extras/ea55620a3199f4afebdaac107dd706db.avif?t=1603896637\" width=616 height=120 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A small puzzle-platformer with a minimalistic and touching story about farewell.<br></li><li>Discover the way to carry your sword to the end of each screen<br></li><li>Explore an ancient cave with 50 levels that mix platforming skills and puzzles<br></li><li>More than 15 secrets scattered through the cave to be found<br></li><li>Small Game: Main game can be completed in less than 1 hour</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1399380/extras/1f9a766d493b06584b68bb03384c58af.avif?t=1603896637\" width=616 height=120 /></span><br><br>NUI is a small passion project made in our free time, for that reason, it is meant to be a short and fun experience.<br>Let us here your thoughts and suggestions about it! Contact us by any of the links available at <br>Have fun playing it!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1399380/extras/30a4ecbe94af55b54f6b1652a459f42d.poster.avif?t=1603896637\" width=616 height=3